rage, 86 new/updated tests this session.\n- **Recurring pattern identified**: AGENTS.md documentation lag is now 3/7 sessions. Recommended embedding it in the dev agent prompt rather than listing it as a retrospective action item that keeps being ignored.\n- **No producer-consumer disconnect** this session -- integration of already-tested components avoids the pattern that hit Sessions 1-5."}],"totalDurationMs":135979,"totalTokens":42770,"totalToolUseCount":8,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":4135,"cache_read_input_tokens":38344,"output_tokens":290,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":4135},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
